post0.title: masks4all
post0.content: The Czech Republic went from zero mask usage to 100% in 10 days, and in the process they halted the growth of new covid-19 cases.How? They made their own! They didn't need government help; they did it themselves.It's time for #masks4all. See why:https://t.co/SiYApRvByq1/ . — Jeremy Howard (@jeremyphoward) March 25, 2020 .
